spec_data.Name: texlive-logical-markup-utils
spec_data.Description:
The bundle contains two packages: quoted, for inserting
quotation marks; and onedash, for inserting dashes. Each
package takes a language name as an option; accepted language
options are american, british, german and polish.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 07:39:49 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Packages for language-dependent inline quotes and dashes
